summary: Adds a bed to Bromjunaar Sanctuary.
descriptionHtml:
The mod adds a bed to the wooden mask wearing version of Bromjunaar Sanctuary. Meaning that if you are using mods that makes sleeping a need, you can now use this location as a functioning hideout or home.

If you are looking for a mod that adds more content like crafting stations, then you might find these mods more usefull:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/9572/?]Bromjunaar Extended[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45513/?]Bromjunaar Sanctuary Reborn[/url]
